94
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,879
It will be different.

95
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,040
Sorry, I also can't.

96
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:28,360
You're really reluctant, huh?

97
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,439
Camping doesn't require

98
