much thinking.

99
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:33,480
Anyone with hands and feet can do it.

100
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,519
Big Hui, right?

101
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,639
Your coffee is great.

102
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:41,959
But I have to go now.

103
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,120
I hope

104
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,160
I'll get to

105
