normal for a few minutes.

113
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,480
Don't bother. I got this.

114
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,319
Why didn't you tell me?

115
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,959
How do I know you hit on her?

116
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,759
Nobody has

117
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:11,800
hit on me for a while.

118
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:12,879
Thanks.

119
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,959
N-No problem.

120
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:30,639
Today,

121
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,040
I visited Dad.

122
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:34,240
Is he okay?

123
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,160
No, he's in a terrible mood.

124
00:06:37,879 --> 00:06:39,160
Last year, I told you

125
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,279
my parents wanted

126
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,240
some money back.

127
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,000
You said after New Year's Day.

128
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:44,199
But

129
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,680
it's almost October.

130
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:50,040
Do they know about the fire accident
at my studio last year?

131
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,199
Of course.

132
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:54,360
So they know

133
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,800
how much the rebuilding costs

134
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,800
and how many pieces I lost.

135
00:06:59,360 --> 00:06:59,959
That's why

136
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,879
I haven't pressed you for ten months.

137
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,759
This is

138
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,199
a tough time.

139
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,560
- We need...
- Right now,

140
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:09,079
you're a master who's come back

141
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,160
with much greater influence.

142
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:12,399
Yeah,

143
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,560
but turning my influence into wealth

144
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,000
still takes time.

145
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:22,800
Fine.

146
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:25,759
I'll wait.

147
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,439
I'll hurry up.

148
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:34,120
Not coming home again?

149
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,279
Yeah.

150
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:37,240
I need to work overtime at the studio.

151
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,199
You know I have so many

152
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,160
undelivered works.

153
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:41,879
Yeah, I know.

154
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,399
You've worked hard.

155
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,680
I'll go upstairs myself.

156
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,240
Don't block the path

157
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,560
with your car.

158
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:00,399
Alright.

159
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,720
Go home

160
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:03,000
and get some rest.

161
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,680
All I do is rest.

162
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:08,720
You're the one who needs rest.

163
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,560
I'm okay.

164
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,000
Don't stay up late.

165
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,560
If anything comes up,

166
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:15,920
call me.

167
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,039
Come on.

168
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,200
What?

169
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,519
I got designated drivers for both of us.

170
00:08:38,209 --> 00:08:41,121
(Designated driver)

171
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,919
Nice.

172
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:44,960
So tell me,

173
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,240
any updates lately?

174
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,279
I toast you.

175
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,480
Big Hui, I told you

176
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,720
that I need something solid

177
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:54,399
to go on.

178
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:56,120
Without any evidence,

179
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:56,759
I really...

180
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,480
I toast to your police badge.

181
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,559
I didn't investigate you.

182
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,879
I just happened to learn that

183
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:06,080
your badge number

184
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,559
was reactivated twice.

185
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,320
(Li Shen)

186
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:26,960
Mom.

187
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:44,519
(Not the police academy!)

188
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:45,759
Dad told you

189
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:47,120
to work on academics or research.

190
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,399
Why the police academy?

191
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,039
Your scores were better.

192
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,960
But you joined the force!

193
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,440
I have to

194
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,879
reactivate Dad's badge number.

195
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,799
I don't want it

196
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,159
to remain archived forever.

197
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,360
Listen to me, okay?

198
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,960
Our family

199
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:15,399
doesn't need a third officer.

200
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,360
Study something else.

201
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,320
It'll put Mom's mind at ease.

202
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,360
(My dad drank with my brother.)

203
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:32,960
I never drank with them.

204
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:34,120
Li De.

205
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:35,879
I respect you.

206
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,080
I respect your whole family.

207
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:43,799
That's enough.

208
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:44,799
I don't

209
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:45,840
want to start crying.

210
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,200
Come on.

211
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,320
Tell me

212
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:50,840
your news.

213
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,279
I met this girl

214
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,799
a few days ago.

215
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:55,799
Well, not exactly.

216
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,799
But we did meet.
I don't have her WeChat.

217
00:10:59,399 --> 00:10:59,879
Wait.

218
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:00,600
What?

219
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,559
Listen.

220
00:11:01,639 --> 00:11:02,200
This girl

221
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,399
is not exactly normal.

222
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:04,960
Good.

223
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,000
Just like you.

224
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:06,799
Come on.

225
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,080
She's...

226
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,279
Did you tell her

227
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,120
that you're

228
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:11,639
looking for your ex-girlfriend?

229
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,200
We didn't talk that much.

230
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,000
I haven't gotten
her contact information.

231
00:11:16,559 --> 00:11:17,519
I'm looking for

232
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,480
my ex-girlfriend?

233
00:11:18,799 --> 00:11:20,240
It's an investigation.

234
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:21,879
Nothing about feelings.

235
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:22,960
You could say

236
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:25,600
i-it's an occupational habit.

237
00:11:25,919 --> 00:11:27,279
Since she's as abnormal as you,

238
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:27,960
she should

239
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,039
understand you.

240
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:31,519
She might even help
look for your ex-girlfriend.

241
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:32,120
No.

242
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:32,919
Investigate.

243
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:33,759
Yeah.

244
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:34,360
Enough.

245
00:11:34,519 --> 00:11:35,440
Whatever you say.

246
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,600
You'll meet her

247
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,759
once I get to know her.

248
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:38,799
Seriously though,

249
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,559
how's your investigation going?

250
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:43,240
I met Zeng Jie the other day.

251
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:44,279
And?

252
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,960
I returned empty-handed.

253
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,039
He's clean?

254
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,679
Absolutely clean,

255
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:52,200
which is exactly the problem.

256
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,200
You see,

257
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:54,240
logically speaking,

258
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,519
