Let me go.

285
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,000
Let me go.

286
00:12:57,159 --> 00:12:58,440
What are you doing? Let me go.

287
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,840
(She was sold to)

288
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,240
(a remote mountain village)

289
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:03,039
(not marked on any map and couldn't be)

290
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,159
(pinned down on one)

291
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:06,559
(to marry a man who's too poor)

292
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:08,960
