293
00:13:09,639 --> 00:13:11,320
(Imagine a college-educated)

294
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:13,440
(beauty streamer who ends up)

295
00:13:14,399 --> 00:13:15,120
(as the wife)

296
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,679
(of a stranger in a village)

297
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,120
(that likely)

